Class PreservingHashMap

              com.vtls.opensource.utilities.PreservingHashMap
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Cloneable, Map
public final class PreservingHashMap
extends LinkedHashMap

An object that maps keys to a List of values. Every addition to this HashMap will preserve any values associated with a given key as elements within a List.
The added getList method returns a unique, sorted List of pair objects of the form ((Object) Key, (List) Value).

Author:
Joe Liversedge
